Package: bme280-reader
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: BME280 sensor reader for Prometheus textfile collector
 Reads temperature, humidity and pressure from a BME280 sensor
 via the Linux IIO subsystem and writes Prometheus metrics in the
 format expected by node_exporter's textfile collector.
 .
 This release ships a hello-world stub to validate the packaging,
 systemd units and filesystem permissions before the real sensor
 reader is introduced.
